notes: In 2020, the books in the collection underwent an inventory. The books were gathered into one place and staff attempted to identify as many as possible. In the past, many books were accepted into the collection without proper documentation. If a book has the name of someone from Murray County it was kept. The other books were kept on a case-by-case basis. Books that did not have an "updated" number were given one starting with the numbers 2020.003. All documentation concerning this inventory can be found in the inventory files.
